{"tid":1064230,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每一個人...心目中永遠有一個難以忘懷嘅人","createTime":"2019-03-16T11:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T11:37:36.000Z","uid":18737,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"012bf8e8921f13ffb9ec4ff2809704ae5b6b3869","tid":1064230,"uid":18737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T11:22:21.000Z","msg":"即使過左幾多年，即使大家之後有過幾多關係，<br />\n即使大家有冇一齊過，即使分開之後仲有冇再聯絡，<br />\n每一次戴起耳機聽住舊歌情歌都會諗起一啲刻骨銘心嘅回憶。<br />\n四年啦，我過得很好，有一個好愛我嘅女朋友，<br />\n我都好愛佢， 我唔愛你啦，<br />\n但係你永遠都會喺我心裏面佔一席位，<br />\n可能你已經唔記得我，可能你男朋友已經掉曬我送俾你嘅禮物，但係我唔會停止諗起你。<br />\n你永遠都係我世界嘅一粒星星，<br />\n一粒永遠都觸摸不到，但指引住我嘅最光嘅星星。<br />\nYou will always be my Sirius<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"2c012fbdea035e1eae718917e193d082bcc0866e","tid":1064230,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T11:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ufre6Xy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfre6Xy.gif&h=c7582b58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3cf50ce695f6c728cba942dc4db0686410a49af5","tid":1064230,"uid":91846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T11:24:38.000Z","msg":"尤其係睇la la land特別有感觸"},{"pid":"384d6d51032fd57f7c07cc693d7baeba1e405c52","tid":1064230,"uid":18737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c012fbdea035e1eae718917e193d082bcc0866e","tid":1064230,"uid":138138,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T11:23:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ufre6Xy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUfre6Xy.gif&h=c7582b58&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"對唔住吖逼你聽我mk式叫春"},{"pid":"8783cbd10e00624e53348222efe357c6eda00c7d","tid":1064230,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"384d6d51032fd57f7c07cc693d7baeba1e405c52","tid":1064230,"uid":18737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c012fbdea035e1eae718917e193d082bcc0866e","ti